00:18:31.279 --> 00:18:33.519
Like a shirt to the back, like meat to the bone.

00:18:33.680 --> 00:18:35.920
Live together, die together.

00:18:36.359 --> 00:18:37.319
That's right.

00:18:37.480 --> 00:18:38.759
So play a round with us today.

00:18:38.759 --> 00:18:40.640
Come on, sit, sit, sit.

00:18:41.119 --> 00:18:42.279
Come on, Boss.

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:43.480
You've got great luck.

00:18:45.240 --> 00:18:45.880
Why are you sitting here?

00:18:45.880 --> 00:18:47.160
Let me play a hand, come on.

00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:48.680
Brother Fan.

00:18:48.759 --> 00:18:50.759
We haven't hung out like this in ages.

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:52.319
Our brotherhood is fading.

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:53.559
