00:19:07.200 --> 00:19:08.319
Go, go, go, get to the door.

00:19:08.319 --> 00:19:09.440
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

00:19:10.359 --> 00:19:11.039
Five Dots.

00:19:12.480 --> 00:19:14.680
What kind of hand is this?

00:19:19.720 --> 00:19:20.319
He's coming, he's coming!

00:19:20.319 --> 00:19:21.279
Who's coming?

00:19:21.640 --> 00:19:22.960
