00:19:24.359 --> 00:19:25.559
We're screwed, we're screwed.

00:19:25.680 --> 00:19:26.720
Hide, quickly!

00:19:27.240 --> 00:19:28.359
What are you afraid of?

00:19:28.559 --> 00:19:29.359
Hide!

