00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:44.119
What are you doing?

00:19:44.599 --> 00:19:45.720
What's your problem?

00:19:45.960 --> 00:19:47.279
What? You're so fierce.

00:19:47.400 --> 00:19:48.319
Our Big Brother...

00:19:52.240 --> 00:19:53.000
What are you yelling for?

00:19:53.119 --> 00:19:54.559
Clearing my throat, practicing vocals

00:19:55.440 --> 00:19:57.359
Just stay out of the card playing business

00:19:57.799 --> 00:19:58.680
Our Big Brother...

00:20:01.119 --> 00:20:02.559
What do you want to say now?

00:20:04.160 --> 00:20:05.599
Nothing, nothing

00:20:06.599 --> 00:20:08.000
What is under this table?

00:20:08.680 --> 00:20:09.720
Nothing, nothing

00:20:11.720 --> 00:20:12.400
Listen up

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:13.839
Within ten minutes,

00:20:14.039 --> 00:20:15.119
everyone present here

00:20:15.359 --> 00:20:17.079
go to the Military Law Office for ten military club strikes.

00:20:17.599 --> 00:20:19.119
If anyone dares not to go,

00:20:19.759 --> 00:20:20.960
they'll be in confinement for half a month.

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:27.839
Big Brother, come out.

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:28.759
Careful

00:20:35.119 --> 00:20:36.160
I said let's not play

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:37.599
You insisted I play

00:20:38.119 --> 00:20:39.799
Now it's like a cat clawing sticky rice cake,

00:20:40.039 --> 00:20:41.240
