00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:42.519
You, a dignified Brigade Commander

00:20:42.640 --> 00:20:43.839
What are you afraid of?

00:20:44.519 --> 00:20:46.119
In the face of military discipline,

00:20:46.559 --> 00:20:48.160
everyone is equal.

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:49.839
If you violate military discipline,

00:20:50.319 --> 00:20:51.519
you have to suffer the consequences.

00:20:52.279 --> 00:20:53.559
The trouble you caused yourself,

00:20:54.039 --> 00:20:55.119
you bear it yourself.

00:21:00.759 --> 00:21:01.359
Money

00:21:01.480 --> 00:21:02.559
My money is still there

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:07.680
Now our butts are going to blossom

00:21:07.839 --> 00:21:09.279
Luckily I didn't throw money in

