Darn it

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:47.799
Trying to fix me?

00:22:59.799 --> 00:23:00.839
Come on, let's play

00:23:02.559 --> 00:23:03.440
Come on

00:23:04.359 --> 00:23:05.400
Where did you get that?

00:23:05.880 --> 00:23:07.240
A cunning rabbit has three burrows

00:23:07.480 --> 00:23:09.079
Mahjong must have three sets

00:23:09.559 --> 00:23:10.799
You still dare to play?

00:23:11.640 --> 00:23:13.839
Brigade Commander Fan just hid under the table

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:15.519
And we got beaten with military clubs

00:23:15.960 --> 00:23:17.279
Right now, my heart is all...

