What are you scared of?

00:23:22.079 --> 00:23:24.039
I don't believe he can keep this up every day

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:25.920
Darn it

00:23:26.039 --> 00:23:27.640
Come on, let's play

00:23:27.759 --> 00:23:29.359
First Brother, forget it

00:23:29.519 --> 00:23:30.200
What?

00:23:30.440 --> 00:23:31.559
Even you are scared?

00:23:34.759 --> 00:23:36.079
Who can ban gambling?

00:23:36.839 --> 00:23:38.839
If anyone can actually eat this mahjong tile,

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:40.000
I will quit gambling.

00:23:40.160 --> 00:23:41.079
Who dares to eat a mahjong tile?

00:23:41.839 --> 00:23:43.160
Don't speak too absolutely

00:23:43.319 --> 00:23:44.000
Maybe,

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:45.400
there really is someone who doesn't believe in fate.

00:23:45.559 --> 00:23:46.480
Empty talk

00:23:46.839 --> 00:23:48.079
I'm not boasting

00:23:48.319 --> 00:23:50.400
If anyone eats this mahjong tile,

00:23:50.680 --> 00:23:51.960
I will take this whole set of mahjong,

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:53.039
and swallow it all.

00:23:57.119 --> 00:23:58.200
You said it

00:23:58.799 --> 00:24:00.559
If anyone dares to eat one mahjong tile,

00:24:01.480 --> 00:24:03.400
you will swallow the whole set.

00:24:05.279 --> 00:24:06.319
I said it

00:24:33.720 --> 00:24:35.720
Carrying a bellows to the camp,

00:24:35.839 --> 00:24:37.079
you're still a bit green.

00:24:37.960 --> 00:24:38.920
Just wait

00:24:46.880 --> 00:24:48.319
First Brother said,

00:24:49.319 --> 00:24:52.160
if anyone eats one mahjong tile,

00:24:52.599 --> 00:24:55.079
he will swallow the whole set.

