And then quit gambling.

00:24:57.359 --> 00:24:59.119
I just ate a mahjong tile

00:24:59.680 --> 00:25:01.119
When it comes to gambling addiction,

00:25:01.799 --> 00:25:03.279
who has a bigger one than me?

00:25:03.720 --> 00:25:04.799
First Brother,

00:25:05.319 --> 00:25:06.599
keep your word.

00:25:07.759 --> 00:25:09.359
Fine, I'll eat it

00:25:11.839 --> 00:25:13.799
Brigade Commander Fan, as per your orders,

