What?

00:25:50.599 --> 00:25:51.480
Choking it down dry?

00:25:52.720 --> 00:25:55.240
Dip it in some sesame sauce, it tastes delicious.

00:26:08.519 --> 00:26:09.319
How is it?

00:26:11.160 --> 00:26:11.920
It's so bitter.

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:13.920
That one is made of coptis.

00:26:14.079 --> 00:26:15.039
Of course it's bitter.

00:26:15.559 --> 00:26:16.799
You eat that Red Dragon.

00:26:16.960 --> 00:26:18.079
Mix in a little sugar.

00:26:18.279 --> 00:26:20.400
I guarantee it'll taste sweet.

00:26:32.960 --> 00:26:33.799
What's wrong?

00:26:34.079 --> 00:26:35.039
Choked on it?

00:26:36.759 --> 00:26:38.960
I prepared Qiong liquor especially for you.

00:26:39.359 --> 00:26:40.880
Here, wash it down.

00:26:48.400 --> 00:26:49.559
This Ba Wan.

00:26:49.640 --> 00:26:51.640
Must be mixed with that chili oil.

00:26:51.759 --> 00:26:53.720
That chili oil has Sichuan pepper and chilies.

00:26:53.720 --> 00:26:54.799
Stir-fried together.

00:26:54.960 --> 00:26:56.119
Authentic Sichuan flavor.

00:26:56.319 --> 00:26:57.680
It tastes excellent.

00:27:09.000 --> 00:27:10.480
How does it taste?

00:27:12.480 --> 00:27:13.160
Bitter.

00:27:13.319 --> 00:27:14.119
Bitter.

00:27:14.680 --> 00:27:16.160
So you know it's bitter.

00:27:17.960 --> 00:27:20.160
Having a troop that can't show its face is what's bitter.

00:27:20.359 --> 00:27:22.240
Being a disgrace is what's bitter.

00:27:22.599 --> 00:27:25.480
Being sloppy and slack is what's bitter.

00:27:26.160 --> 00:27:28.400
If the troops can't win battles,

00:27:28.519 --> 00:27:30.039
losing face is what's bitter.

00:27:38.480 --> 00:27:39.440
You eat some.

00:27:44.839 --> 00:27:46.519
You were smiling just now.

00:27:47.680 --> 00:27:48.519
Eat some.

00:27:49.079 --> 00:27:50.720
I just had lunch, I'm very full.

00:27:50.839 --> 00:27:52.079
It hasn't gone down yet.

00:27:58.240 --> 00:27:59.160
Eat some.

00:28:03.039 --> 00:28:04.480
Will you guys still gamble?

00:28:04.799 --> 00:28:06.119
No gambling.

00:28:06.359 --> 00:28:07.359
Gamble or not?

00:28:07.519 --> 00:28:09.160
Absolutely not.

00:28:09.440 --> 00:28:10.359
Good.

00:28:10.880 --> 00:28:12.000
Brothers.

00:28:13.720 --> 00:28:15.720
From today on, we get tough.

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:18.519
Training must be done properly.

00:28:18.720 --> 00:28:21.079
We must make a name for ourselves in battle.

00:28:21.160 --> 00:28:22.400
Yes, sir!

00:28:42.359 --> 00:28:43.599
Come catch me.

00:28:47.240 --> 00:28:48.519
Come catch me.

00:28:55.640 --> 00:28:56.599
Brother.

00:28:57.400 --> 00:28:58.200
Brother.

00:28:58.839 --> 00:28:59.559
Something happened.

00:28:59.640 --> 00:29:00.599
Something happened.

00:29:01.200 --> 00:29:02.079
What?

00:29:02.759 --> 00:29:03.759
Xiu Gu.

00:29:03.759 --> 00:29:06.079
She ran off with that Troupe Leader.

00:29:10.160 --> 00:29:11.440
I saw that coming long ago.

00:29:11.640 --> 00:29:13.720
Those two have always had something going on.

00:29:13.960 --> 00:29:15.079
Why didn't you say so earlier?

00:29:16.119 --> 00:29:17.319
You were rising in the ranks.

00:29:17.400 --> 00:29:19.359
Who would've thought she'd stray?

00:29:19.599 --> 00:29:20.720
Go catch her, quick.

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:21.559
Roger that.

00:29:35.920 --> 00:29:36.480
Brother.

00:29:36.880 --> 00:29:37.720
How about we tie them up,

00:29:37.720 --> 00:29:38.480
tie them to a stone,

00:29:38.599 --> 00:29:39.640
and throw them into the pond.

00:29:39.960 --> 00:29:40.640
Do you believe

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:42.599
I'll kill you all right now?

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:43.480
Let him go.

00:29:44.079 --> 00:29:45.240
It was all my idea.

00:29:45.640 --> 00:29:46.880
Kill me or cut me, do as you please.

00:29:47.559 --> 00:29:48.240
Xiu Gu.

00:29:48.640 --> 00:29:49.640
If we die, we die together.

00:29:49.920 --> 00:29:50.880
I'm not afraid.

00:30:00.839 --> 00:30:02.880
Think it over carefully.

00:30:09.960 --> 00:30:10.720
Scarface.

00:30:10.960 --> 00:30:11.759
Give me the gun.

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:13.519
Brother, let me handle this.

00:30:13.759 --> 00:30:14.559
Give it here.

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:19.960
None of you are allowed to follow.

00:30:20.519 --> 00:30:21.519
Stay right here.

00:30:21.920 --> 00:30:22.640
Move.

00:30:33.119 --> 00:30:33.920
Stop right there.

00:30:35.680 --> 00:30:38.240
Think this through carefully.

00:30:46.640 --> 00:30:47.559
Brother Fan.

00:30:49.720 --> 00:30:51.640
You're the first man to ever move my heart.

00:30:53.759 --> 00:30:56.079
I willingly became your concubine.

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:59.519
I followed you through life and death.

00:31:01.160 --> 00:31:02.240
I never once thought...

00:31:02.240 --> 00:31:03.839
...of replacing Sister Yu Zhen.

00:31:05.480 --> 00:31:07.559
I just wanted to be with you, to care for you.

00:31:09.079 --> 00:31:10.039
But what about you?

00:31:13.759 --> 00:31:15.400
You pushed me far away.

00:31:16.480 --> 00:31:18.559
Your eyes are cold when you look at me.

00:31:20.079 --> 00:31:21.039
You avoid me.

00:31:22.519 --> 00:31:23.519
You reject me.

00:31:24.640 --> 00:31:26.319
The only reason I stayed with you...

00:31:26.319 --> 00:31:28.000
...was to avenge my father.

00:31:32.079 --> 00:31:33.799
You're a high-ranking official now.

00:31:33.799 --> 00:31:35.880
Yet you say your hands are tied.

00:31:38.200 --> 00:31:39.279
You know me.

00:31:40.319 --> 00:31:41.039
I've always been this way.

00:31:41.039 --> 00:31:42.799
Love is love, and hate is hate.

00:31:42.920 --> 00:31:44.319
I know when to let go.

00:31:47.279 --> 00:31:49.160
I have no reason to follow you anymore.

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:58.960
I've made up my mind.

00:32:00.480 --> 00:32:01.440
Go ahead, do it.

00:32:12.359 --> 00:32:13.200
You two...

00:32:14.480 --> 00:32:15.720
walk away from here.

00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:17.640
Take ten steps.

00:32:18.640 --> 00:32:19.720
I'll fire three shots.

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:22.480
If I miss you...

00:32:23.720 --> 00:32:25.079
...then run for your lives.

00:32:25.599 --> 00:32:27.079
Don't torture us like this.

00:32:27.799 --> 00:32:28.720
Just get it over with.

00:32:29.960 --> 00:32:31.359
I said go!

00:32:58.039 --> 00:32:59.720
I'm out of practice.

00:33:30.480 --> 00:33:31.200
You two...

00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:33.839
...live a good life.

00:33:34.680 --> 00:33:36.160
Go as far away as you can.

00:33:37.279 --> 00:33:38.279
In this lifetime...

00:33:40.079 --> 00:33:41.880
...don't let me ever see you again.

00:33:43.720 --> 00:33:44.599
And don't let...

00:33:44.599 --> 00:33:46.279
...my men see you either.

00:33:48.359 --> 00:33:50.039
Go on.

00:34:11.079 --> 00:34:12.680
Darn it.

00:34:13.319 --> 00:34:15.760
It tears my heart out.